Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.46,0:01:49.46,Default,T,0,0,0,,Here's another draft.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.04,0:01:55.09,Default,T,0,0,0,,Might not be perfect, but it's what I chose.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.51,Default,S,0,0,0,,It's terrible, but it's hilarious!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.47,Default,S,0,0,0,,You can buy what's in someone's brain?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.72,Default,T,0,0,0,,Terrible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.72,0:02:06.31,Default,T,0,0,0,,I know this kind of thing \Nwouldn't work for Jack though.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.31,0:02:08.02,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,There he is. Takagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.35,Default,T,0,0,0,,Hey Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.98,Default,T,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you leave the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.78,0:02:14.44,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.57,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,Let's go after school today, \Na welcome-back present.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.57,0:02:17.45,Default,T,0,0,0,,Can't.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.45,0:02:21.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,I have a meeting at Yueisha today to \Ngo over our Tezuka Award submission.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.16,0:02:21.91,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,Then tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.91,0:02:22.78,Default,T,0,0,0,,Can't.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.78,0:02:26.12,Default,T,0,0,0,,We're gonna start our next work \Nusing the feedback from the meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.12,0:02:27.46,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,But Takagi—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.71,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,We're going out, aren't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.54,Default,T,0,0,0,,But didn't you say—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.63,0:02:34.42,Default,T,0,0,0,,My dream to become a \Nmangaka comes first!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.01,Default,T,0,0,0,,Love comes second!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.88,Default,T,0,0,0,,Even if we went out, I wouldn't \Nhave time to actually go on dates!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.97,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,That's fine. I'll support you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.39,0:02:44.31,Default,T,0,0,0,,to me before?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.31,0:02:46.60,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's just for a little bit—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.10,0:02:48.89,Default,T,0,0,0,,Don't you get it, Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.73,Default,T,0,0,0,,I have a dream to become a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.73,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm even imposing on Saiko to help me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.90,Default,T,0,0,0,,I don't have time to go on—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.07,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,But you need a break \Nevery now and then, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.49,Default,T,0,0,0,,Not right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.49,0:02:58.53,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,Not even a small break?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.53,0:02:59.57,Default,T,0,0,0,,Not even a small break.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.16,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,Not even a teeny, tiny break?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.03,Default,T,0,0,0,,Not even a teeny, tiny break!
