Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.10,0:24:23.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,N—Niizuma?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.52,0:24:25.56,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Next time: Chocolate and NEXT!
